text:
Mmm...
Still a bit tricky, ain't it?

Dancin' all bunny-like, hoppin' 'round,
been practicin' that!

But darn, them heels are so high,
can't quite jump right...

Well... I'm glad you're practicing hard,
but don't overdo it, okay?

Yeah~ Thanks, Producer!
Just about to figure somethin' out, so I'll keep at it~!
